[STACK]
- Next.js (App Router)
- React Three Fiber (for background / depth layer)
- GSAP (ScrollTrigger + motion control)

[RENDERING]
- WebGL canvas as background layer
- DOM layered on top

[ANIMATION_RULES]
- No CSS-only animations for core interactions
- Use GSAP or requestAnimationFrame

[PERFORMANCE]
- Memoize heavy components
- Lazy load 3D scene
- Limit particle count

[STRUCTURE]
/components
  /scene
  /ui
  /motion
/hooks
  useMouseParallax
  useFloat